    dek: `Good sound is one of the best-value investments in indie film, because the gear that gets you 90% of the way is genuinely affordable — and the last, most important ingredient is free. Here's a realistic budget kit, the DIY tricks that punch above their price, and where your money is actually worth spending.`,
